Name: Element Section Skateboard
Description: Professional 8.25-inch skateboard deck crafted from 7-ply Canadian maple with medium concave. Features precision aluminum trucks, 99A urethane wheels, and high-speed bearings. Perfect for street and park skating with reliable performance.

Name: Santa Cruz Classic Cruiser
Description: Vintage-style 10-inch cruiser board with classic dot graphic. Made from 9-ply maple with old-school shape and kicktail. Equipped with 60mm 78A soft wheels for smooth rides on rough pavement. Great for commuting.

Name: Plan B Team Deck 8.0
Description: Professional 8.0-inch deck designed for technical street skating. Features steep concave for maximum control and lightweight construction with 7-ply maple. Ideal for flip tricks and advanced maneuvers.

Name: Almost Impact Plus Deck
Description: Innovative 8.125-inch deck with carbon fiber reinforcement technology. 50% stronger construction prevents breakage while maintaining traditional flex. Medium concave with radial bend for comfortable control.

Name: Baker 8.5 Pro Model
Description: Wide 8.5-inch deck designed for transition skating and big gaps. Extra width provides stability at high speeds. Mellow concave comfortable for long sessions. Perfect for park and vert skating.

Name: Mini Logo Beginner Deck
Description: Affordable 7.75-inch deck perfect for beginners and younger riders. Made from 7-ply maple with medium concave. Simple design with quality construction at accessible price point.

Name: Thrasher Flame Beanie
Description: Classic skate beanie with Thrasher Magazine flame logo. Premium acrylic blend provides warmth without itchiness. One-size-fits-most with stretch construction. Essential skate accessory.

Name: Carhartt Watch Beanie
Description: Durable workwear beanie made from 100% acrylic. Rib-knit design provides stretch and warmth. Reinforced edge binding won't unravel. Perfect for fall and winter sessions.

Name: Supreme Box Logo Beanie
Description: Premium wool blend beanie with Supreme's iconic box logo. 80% wool and 20% acrylic for optimal warmth. Dense knit construction with wind resistance. Limited edition.

Name: Mechanix Work Gloves
Description: Professional-grade gloves for skateboard maintenance. Synthetic leather with breathable spandex back. Padded palms for impact protection. Touchscreen-compatible index finger.

Name: Hestra Ski Gloves
Description: Waterproof Gore-Tex gloves for winter skateboarding. 40g insulation provides warmth in freezing conditions. Pre-curved fingers reduce fatigue. Adjustable wrist strap.

Name: Burton Gore-Tex Mittens
Description: Snowboard mittens with Gore-Tex waterproof technology. Mitt design keeps fingers together for maximum warmth. Articulated thumb for natural grip. Durable palm material.

Name: Arc'teryx Windproof Gloves
Description: Technical windproof gloves made from Windstopper fabric. Minimal insulation maintains dexterity. Silicone grip pattern on palm enhances control. Perfect for chilly weather.

Name: Vans SK8-Hi Pro Shoes
Description: Iconic high-top skate shoes with Pro construction. Suede and canvas upper with reinforced toe caps. UltraCush HD insoles for impact protection. Waffle outsole for superior grip.

Name: Nike SB Dunk Low
Description: Legendary skateboarding sneaker combining basketball heritage with skate performance. Premium leather and suede construction. Zoom Air unit for responsive cushioning. Classic silhouette.

Name: Adidas Busenitz Pro
Description: Professional model designed with Dennis Busenitz. Full-grain leather upper with reinforced toe and heel. Cupsole construction for impact protection. Classic three-stripe design.

Name: Converse CONS CTS
Description: Vulcanized skate shoe with Nike Zoom Air cushioning. Canvas and suede upper with reinforced toe cap. CONS rubber outsole offers grip and flexibility. Mid-top design.

Name: Etnies Marana Michelin
Description: Ultra-durable skate shoe with Michelin rubber outsole technology. Exceptional rubber compound for extended wear. STI Evolution foam for impact protection. Water-resistant treatment.

Name: New Balance Numeric 440
Description: Technical skate shoe designed for precision and control. Pig suede and ripstop upper for durability. Cush+ insole for comfort. Ndurance rubber outsole for wear resistance.

Name: Emerica Romero Laced
Description: Classic cupsole skate shoe with vulcanized-style board feel. Premium suede upper with reinforced stitching. STI foam system for impact protection. Gum rubber outsole for grip.
